data.name: labeldfHeadingMandToPi.Text
data.value: Welcome to the Direct Debiting Mandate File Creation Wizard. This wizard will guide you how to create a direct debiting mandate file. Before the wizard is run, basic data such as external file type and external file template definitions should be created. The execution can be performed either online or in batch.

data.name: labeldfHeadingCurrUpd.Text
data.value: Welcome to the Automatic Currency Update Wizard. This wizard will guide you how to read and process an external automatic currency update input file or how to create an external automatic currency update output file. Before the wizard is started basic data such as external file type and external file template definitions must have been created. The execution can be performed either in online or in batch mode.
